            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "台幣置身於全球市場震盪之外 大型出口商與公股銀行扮演穩盤角色",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 正當全球金融市場因地緣政治緊張情緒波動放大之際，近日<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:台幣;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/台幣\">台幣</a>尚能維持穩定於小幅區間，且兩周期的歷史波動率在主要亞幣裡僅高於港元與人民幣，主因本地匯市的美元供、需動態平衡。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據多位外匯交易員表示，在本周二與周三外資匯出主導台幣貶值，日內跌幅擴大之際，看到大型出口商賣出美元與外資對作，達到限制台幣貶勢的作用，公股銀行則於尾盤流動性較低的時候繼續賣出美元，進一步收斂台幣貶幅。而通常當市場參與者看見一家大型出口商大量賣出美元後，買入美元/台幣的報價就不再繼續上行。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-bcc8cd6f-b723-39ef-a2e1-760ebf51d434-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/EHBhZaW5hvwIdttYeAGkKA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/824943d02e7a1029cdc764f9300c15f7\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">反之當台幣走勢偏升時美元買盤也會伺機出沒。其中一位交易員稱，上周當外資匯入較多時, 亦看到壽險業的美元買盤出籠。上述交易員不願具名接受採訪，因未被授權公開評論。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據彭博數據，台幣一個月期隱含波動度於周四降至逾9個月新低，與其他亞幣波動度升高的情況逆勢而行。另外，就兩周期的主要亞幣歷史波動率來觀察，台幣只高於定錨美元的港元，以及受到較多監管的人民幣。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">台幣兌美元在最近10個交易日裡陷於31.494-31.706的區間拉鋸，穩定走勢反映出，儘管外資進出仍是匯率走勢的主導因素，但具指標性的市場參與者的行為可以有效使匯價免於過度波動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國銀行於報告指出，美元供需平衡的狀態使得台幣目前相對穩定，預期第一季將延續低波動的態勢，不過任何來自於美國財政部對於台幣估值過低的評論為潛在風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8F%B0%E5%B9%A3%E7%BD%AE%E8%BA%AB%E6%96%BC%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E9%9C%87%E7%9B%AA%E4%B9%8B%E5%A4%96-%E5%A4%A7%E5%9E%8B%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%95%86%E8%88%87%E5%85%AC%E8%82%A1%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E6%89%AE%E6%BC%94%E7%A9%A9%E7%9B%A4%E8%A7%92%E8%89%B2-081409014.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-22 16:54:55",
