        {
            "title": "全球晶片股勁揚 輝達CEO在達沃斯的講話增強AI交易熱情",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 全球半導體股上漲，輝達公司執行長黃仁勳在達沃斯論壇的講話進一步增強了投資者對人工智能交易主題的熱情。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">記憶晶片製造商三星電子周四一度漲逾6%，觸及歷史新高，並推動韓國基準Kospi指數首次站上5,000點。受輝達股價上漲提振，費城半導體指數周三上漲超過3%，創下新高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在川普表示將不對反對美國獲得格陵蘭的歐洲國家加徵關稅後，市場風險情緒整體回升。黃仁勳的講話進一步助推了漲勢，他在世界經濟論壇上表示，全球人工智能建設將需要數萬億美元的投資。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-ac17e3f4-23d4-3ad2-9dcb-878a1fb02c78-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Mf309VkP0CILeM7Sw_6zRA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/ea265289f649ba5d96bad98540a979d2\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">英特爾將於周四晚些時候發布財報，可能會進一步披露關鍵的行業資本支出計畫。蘋果公司和Meta Platforms Inc.下周將公佈業績。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Disco Corp.在東京飆升17%，該晶片設備製造商發布的盈利數據好於預期。台積電上漲1.7%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Global Chip Stocks Soar as Huang Helps Fuel AI Euphoria at Davos</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E6%99%B6%E7%89%87%E8%82%A1%E5%8B%81%E6%8F%9A-%E8%BC%9D%E9%81%94ceo%E5%9C%A8%E9%81%94%E6%B2%83%E6%96%AF%E7%9A%84%E8%AC%9B%E8%A9%B1%E5%A2%9E%E5%BC%B7ai%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E7%86%B1%E6%83%85-050914283.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-22 13:46:19",
