        {
            "title": "烏克蘭總統澤連斯基據悉前往達沃斯與川普會面",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 一位知情人士透露，烏克蘭總統沃洛迪米爾·<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:澤連斯基;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/澤連斯基\">澤連斯基</a>正在前往達沃斯的途中，他周四將和美國總統唐納德·川普會面。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澤連斯基本周早些時候表示，他不太可能前往世界經濟論壇年會，因為他正在指揮應對俄羅斯大規模空襲的行動，這些空襲導致基輔和其他幾個地區的大片區域在嚴寒的冬季沒有暖氣、電力和水。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然而川普周三表示，他將在瑞士這個滑雪勝地會見澤連斯基。澤連斯基此前曾表示，如果美烏雙方能夠就安全保障和振興烏克蘭經濟的計畫達成協議，他將重新考慮是否前往。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-75edacc4-863e-36d5-a6ff-50bdfd524ac1-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此外，美國特使史蒂夫· 威特科夫和賈裡德·庫什納周四將前往俄羅斯與總統弗拉基米爾·普丁會面，商討關於結束烏克蘭戰爭的最新和平計畫方案。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Ukraine President Zelenskiy Heads to Davos to Meet With Trump</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%83%8F%E5%85%8B%E8%98%AD%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E6%BE%A4%E9%80%A3%E6%96%AF%E5%9F%BA%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E5%89%8D%E5%BE%80%E9%81%94%E6%B2%83%E6%96%AF%E8%88%87%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%9C%83%E9%9D%A2-073052901.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-22 16:16:41",
