        },
        {
            "title": "對沖基金Gen2在與三星證券的糾紛中尋求1.37億美元賠償",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 總部位於香港的對沖基金Gen2 Partners Ltd.尋求向三星的三家金融公司索賠逾1.37億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博新聞看到的訴狀副本顯示，Gen2 Funds本周在香港高等法院對三星證券、Samsung Hedge Asset Management Co.和Samsung Securities (Asia) Ltd.提起索賠。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">訴訟涉及新冠疫情期間市場動盪引發的一起合同糾紛。當時，一支Gen2基金暫停了贖回，以保護投資者和基金自身利益。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-34f9e88b-576e-3732-95ff-332d924989b0-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Gen2稱這些三星實體及其員工的行為給其造成了損失，因而尋求賠償和禁令救濟。該對沖基金指控它們擾亂了基金運營，對其與主經紀商的融資安排造成不利影響，迫使其清算資產，導致投資者蒙受損失並損害了其聲譽。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Hedge Fund Seeks $137 Million in Dispute With Samsung Securities</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Youkyung Lee、Cat Barton、Yoolim Lee.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B0%8D%E6%B2%96%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91gen2%E5%9C%A8%E8%88%87%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E8%AD%89%E5%88%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%B3%BE%E7%B4%9B%E4%B8%AD%E5%B0%8B%E6%B1%821-37%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E8%B3%A0%E5%84%9F-062243096.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-22 15:06:14",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        }
